 the Vehicle Management Code. For your own safety, I strongly advise discontinuing all such modifications.","quest_name":"What Burns Beneath Frostlands","quest_id":915000001},{"text":"I must note that the student committed major Vehicle Management Code violations and breached dozens of school regulations. Severe disciplinary action was taken.","quest_name":"What Burns Beneath Frostlands","quest_id":915000001},{"text":"Hm—","quest_name":"What Burns Beneath Frostlands","quest_id":915000001}]}